			('Dine In', 'High-speed Wi-Fi Internet', 'CCTV Surveillance', 'Drinks Available', 'Smoking Zone',
			'Vallet Parking', 'Alcohol Served', 'Buffet', 'Pure Veg', 'Outdoor Seating', 'Inhouse Catering',
